  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Armor Master's Handbook pg. 27</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> strong enchantment <strong>CL</strong> 13th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> armor quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>Armor with the <em>terrain-striding</em> special ability is attuned to a specific terrain when the armor is created, selected from rangers' favored terrains. The wearer of armor gains a 10-foot enhancement bonus to her speed while in the associated terrain, and the armor's armor check penalty does not apply to Acrobatics, Climb, and Stealth checks attempted in that terrain. The <em>terrain-striding</em> special ability can be applied only to medium armor.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>resistance</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus</p>",
